      <title>新加坡元在政策收紧观点下创下 2024 年新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/sgd-usd-singapore-dollar-advances-toward-18-month-high-on-rate-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于预测新加坡央行今年将采取相对于美联储更为紧缩的货币政策，新加坡元兑美元延续涨势，创下 2024 年新高，这有利于新加坡元兑美元汇率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/sgd-usd-singapore-dollar-advances-toward-18-month-high-on-rate-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 04:18:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
